OL,8,G1700FDiscovering: Jon Voight
OL,9,     GHe's an Academy Award-winning
OL,10,     Gactor who starred in Deliverance
OL,11,     Gand Coming Home, and the father
OL,12,     Gof Hollywood star Angelina Jolie.
OL,13,     GThis is the story of Jon Voight.
OL,14,G1800FTales Of The Unexpected
OL,15,     GSound Machine: Klausner is a
OL,16,     Gbotanist who has invented a
OL,17,     Gmachine that can translate the
OL,18,     Gsounds of trees and plants into
OL,19,     Gintelligible speech, but he is
OL,20,     Gshocked by what he hears.
